This paper deals with control-affine continuous-time nonlinear systems, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). The paper also uses reinforcement learning techniques, which is a popular topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of a system identifier also suggests a connection to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper deals with convergence analysis, which is a common theme in neural networks (cs.NE).
